With easy access to major highways, this gem offers the perfect balance between suburban tranquility and urban convenience.

Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the desirable Green Oaks neighborhood. With a selling price of $800,000, this 2,000 sqft home is the perfect blend of comfort and style. The spacious kitchen features stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, making it a chef's dream. The master bedroom has a luxurious en-suite bathroom with a walk-in shower and separate soaking tub. Step outside to the serene backyard with a patio and a lush lawn. 

Green Oaks is a vibrant community known for its eco-friendly lifestyle. Surrounded by organic grocery stores, community gardens, and bike paths, you'll experience sustainable living at its finest. Spend your weekends exploring the nearby Green Oaks Park or sipping coffee at the cozy Green Bean Cafe. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to public transportation and bike lanes. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Green Oaks gem your new home.
